menu_items.product_name: Sarson Da Saag With Makki Di Roti Lunchbox
menu_items.small_description: Steeped in nostalgia and the rustic charm of the northern countryside, this culinary masterpiece is a must have during winters. Served alongside a golden Makke di roti and a dollop of butter, this dish carries the warmth of home, the spirit of celebration, and the essence of Punjab's rich culinary heritage.
